      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 80,
      "message": "I think I would prefer to leave it as it is to be honest. As I already commented when reviewing your merge request I'm not sure why we're mixing all possible models (VNF, VF module, PNF) and types of executions (DE, BB) in 1 class (GeneratePayloadForCds). I don't understand to be honest why we need routing through this class as it only adds another layer of complexity. Practically the only thing that our implementation has in common is prepareAndSetCdsPropertyBean() which could be extracted to separate class. In my personal opinion current class hierarchy is bit complex with additional switches and routings.",
